Download Karel from http://www.csis.pace.edu/~bergin/KarelJava2ed/downloads.html

Install BlueJ from website: www.bluej.org

Get karelmain.java example program from http://kbucaria.com/html/java/KarelMain.java
-adjust Ur_robot to UrRobot.

Then follow Simulatoruserguide.pdf for getting Karel to work with BlueJ

Then insert karelmain.java code into new Karel project in BlueJ and run it.
